CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 22, 1967, pg. 13, reads: "Makes Introduction - Mrs. James Shelton, (left) president of the Squaws, took time out to introduce new members Mrs. Richard..., Mrs. Harry Bluett, and Mrs Dozia Frazier, Jr. ...during intermission.
TitMainTitle: Squaw members, from left: Mrs. James Shelton, Mrs. Richard [unknown], Mrs. Harry Bluett, and Mrs. Dozia Frazier Jr., posed in Hilton Hotel for "Cotton Extravaganza"
